      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZOOLU (8) drew very wide so wasn't disgraced in her latest attempt in the G1 NSW Trotters Oaks at Menangle. Had kicked off her campaign with a Maryborough win prior and scored the only time she raced here so she is much better placed dropping in grade. Draws for a trail so if she gets the gaps she can go close. LEANNE LEEANN (6) was good when placed in a higher-girded race at Geelong last start. Draws wider but also recorded back-to-back placings earlier this month so could be close to another win. ROMANTIC NINA (7) had to work last start so prepared to forgive that result. May need luck from this draw but she placed in her previous three outings so is worth another chance. BUCKLES FOR BERRY (3) scored from a back row draw here two back before drawing wider than this when midfield last start. Race fit now and aided by a favourable draw.",
